TITLE.P: Dynamic Purchasing System (DPS) 13/23DL for International Higher Education Student Recruitment for Atlantic Technological University

SHORT_DESCR.P: ATU wishes to establish a Dynamic Purchasing System (DPS) of Education Agents to support the recruitment of non-EU students across all campuses. All applicants who provide the information in the Qualification Questionnaire contained in Appendix 1, who clearly demonstrate they operate within this service area will be considered for admittance to the DPS.
